Ive grouped with one dwarven cleric in OOP (forgot name, sorry) that had full kunark armor set and with buffs he had over 1100ac and a CLERIC!<br>
<br>
I talked to a lvl 60 halfling warrior in FoH on veeshan that had very near 1300ac buffed <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
But id try and get 200wis, then 1k ac, then mana.<br>
