<br>
-Stalpus <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/ulaurri.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Laurri</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 52<br> <font color=#6FB8DD>(6/4/01 2:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernclassdiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=101.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.travelersofnorrath.com/Laurri.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re:  AC or MANA @ lvl 60?</span><hr size=1> Im a 58 cleric.  I spoke to a lot of high level clerics as I was making my way up the ranks, and there seems to be 2 schools of thought on gear.<br>
<br>
Both agree that you want your 200wis as your first priority.<br>
<br>
School 1: AC AC AC AC....what good is a dead cleric?<br>
<br>
School 2: Mana gear...manage your aggro carefully and carry mana to burn.<br>
<br>
I run a lot of raids.  The clerics that are assigned casters and leather/chain melee classes would be better off with mana gear since they rarely pull aggro with big CH's but need to do lots of healing when there group isnt paying attention to aggro management.<br>
<br>
Those grouped with the main tank want AC because sometimes you're forced to CH the puller on arrival and big bad thing jumps straight off the tank and onto the cleric.<br>
<br>
<br>
Personally I buff with self buffs only to 1055 ac.  I carry 2 sets of gear...ac and resist.  I dont go with mana gear because too often I am in the main group and get beat on a LOT.<br>
<br>
<br>
One other note...there is some chatter about wisdom affecting how well your spells land.  Much like CHA affects mez/charm for chanters/bards/druids,   WIS may affect how well your STUNS land.  This as far as I know is unconfirmed, but Im experimenting.<br>
<br>
<br>
Laurri <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/udarizrahae.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DarizraHAE</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 46<br> <font color=#6FB8DD>(6/4/01 2:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernclassdiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=101.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re:  AC or MANA @ lvl 60?</span><hr size=1> Lately ive been playing around with my gear, and I'm starting to think after 200wis and 1000ish AC(buffed) it will be alot more usefull to go  with more HP/AC. <br>
