<br>
At 60 with my enchanter i easily approach the 800ac mark, however, ac means dick when a mob is clawing me for 500points a pop(sometimes even more) My best bet to stay alive at that point is HP all the way. So with the right gear and buffs i easily hit 3500hp. Yes you read that correctly. <br>
<br>
So it's all a matter of choice, however, look at how hard you are getting hit and tell me if added ac means anything =)<br>
